{"tid":1159282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國瑜：台灣不參與聯合國 能發大財","createTime":"2019-05-17T14:28:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-17T17:32:51.000Z","uid":144372,"like":1,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2f1a873dfb585a968c34506fcb80800c28c2bb2d","tid":1159282,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T14:28:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20190517004074-260407\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20190517004074-260407&d=LRk9npnliL4HefRMP%2BWOkMTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=7d7d209c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20190517004074-260407</a><br />\n<br />\n針對2020總統大選，韓國瑜今天接受《旺旺中時媒體集團》專訪，再拋新議題，強調下屆總統要有創意，像過去大家感嘆台灣不是聯合國會員，其實只要轉換思考，「劣勢也能變優勢」，正因我們非會員，只要符合文明國家標準，其實可以不受聯合國規範，「自有很多『空隙及彈性』！」<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜17日下午接受中天、中國時報、旺報、周刊王聯合專訪，他自稱「18歲以後沒怕過，現在60歲只怕台灣怎麼變這樣」，他表示，我國非聯合國會員，許多組織無法參加，外交處處碰壁，邦交國說斷就斷，國際空間愈來愈狹隘，眼看周邊的國家、地區開始經濟整合，台灣卻形單影隻，處境艱困。<br />\n<br />\n但他反向思考，台灣可發揮非聯合國會員的優勢，「運用之妙，存乎一心」，腦袋一打開來，剎那間發現原來我們也有巨大優勢，沒被聯合國規範，只需接受世界文明國家的標準，當中就有「空隙」及「彈性」，正好是台灣可發展的時機。<br />\n<br />\n他舉例，一旦跳脫規範，假設全世界有錢人要放錢，覺得歐洲就放在瑞士，亞洲就放台灣，認定台灣是最安全的地方；此外，全世界各國商船、郵輪都不再只是登記在巴拿馬，也可能選擇登記中華民國。<br />\n<br />\n「我知道說了之後，接下來又有網軍要黑我！」韓國瑜說，對於如何跳脫聯合國規範，他腦中已有想法，但一旦表述馬上會招來批判，罵他只會跳脫式思考；他認為，領導者若沒創意，只會呆板行事，如何突破台灣發展困境。"},{"pid":"2dc1b57bb9d30123586c8565c7f30bcd4d3cadc2","tid":1159282,"uid":36383,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T14:31:30.000Z","msg":"腦袋一打開來，發現韓國魚是冇腦袋的"},{"pid":"0fe3980690b4eb5416df7d1f42db4ec2adbd7e0f","tid":1159282,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T14:32:50.000Z","msg":"以為自己係邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3475fce9a70eb65ef4dd7c008461ac36897d5e05","tid":1159282,"uid":20867,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T14:34:55.000Z","msg":"陳雲根：（癲撚過我🙄）"},{"pid":"9ce533d998683d82fcb98d8c43717474ef33404d","tid":1159282,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T14:38:38.000Z","msg":"草包+土包"},{"pid":"a69fa154802e2f81100d8b537148f4665948285c","tid":1159282,"uid":13689,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T14:39:34.000Z","msg":"Marvel發大財<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"220e9c913a935abf42f52f0fd51cdfe7a725fa82","tid":1159282,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T14:42:00.000Z","msg":"念力"},{"pid":"5d95a72afb077cb75b07b7c99ec6970c554b3ab9","tid":1159282,"uid":23993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T14:48:50.000Z","msg":"鳩噏發大財<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f70f951a447233aae3d2d6aca038aeb66dd10c3b","tid":1159282,"uid":4942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T14:49:57.000Z","msg":"白痴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到底佢明唔明入聯合國有咩著數"},{"pid":"a37123f01d4e95dd41d43be4ac6c8ce10447b172","tid":1159282,"uid":47135,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T14:52:13.000Z","msg":"條友全年都係新年mood <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n發大財<br />\n大<br />\n財"},{"pid":"986bd2e396e6374bc5274b02694bba894eb94651","tid":1159282,"uid":6293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T14:52:45.000Z","msg":"台灣點會係最安全嘅地方呀大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6c48cdb0e150eea4a4c5d84ced6796b1d7c4744","ti